name: Lady Veiled in Blood, Photograph, by @VicDeLeon
description: Digital Photograph of the 8” x 2.5” sculpture by @VicDeLeon Lady Veiled in Blood (Femme Voilée de Sang) Digitally sculpted by artist Vic DeLeon and printed using sterilized human blood drawn from the artist, combined with treated photochemical bio-resin. Based on La Femme Voilée by master sculptor Antonio Corradini c.1700. FORMAT: Uncompressed PNG Image 3000x3000. more info at https://www.instagram.com/p/CIJdPKsJXii/  Artist Twitter: @VicDeLeon
